). Fixed digit 31 ( 30–32 ) long with five visible teeth, with pilus dentilis ; movable digit 31 ( 30–32 ) long with one tooth.

Spermatheca (
Figure 4
). Calyx cup-shaped, 11 ( 10–12 ) long; atrium nodular, slightly forked; major duct broad, minor duct visible.

